# Response Template

## Required Response Format

Every technical answer must start with:

```
📚 **Documentation Check:**
- ✅ Read: docs/svelte 5/svelte.md
- ✅ Read: docs/svelte 5/svelte_rules.md
- ✅ Read: [other relevant docs]

**Based on your local documentation:** [answer here]
```

## If External Sources Needed:
```
📚 **Documentation Check:**
- ✅ Read: [local files]
- ❌ Local docs don't cover [specific topic]
- 🌐 Supplementing with: [external source]
```

## Template Example:
```
📚 **Documentation Check:**
- ✅ Read: docs/svelte 5/svelte.md (lines 11335-11381)
- ✅ Found SvelteMap information in your local docs

**Based on your local documentation:** SvelteMap is imported from 'svelte/reactivity'...
```

This format makes it impossible to forget the documentation check step.